==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: home-schooled
<hw>home-schooled</hw> <pos>a.</pos> <def>Receiving or having received
formal education, especially primary or secondary education, at home
rather than in a school. The instruction at home may be accomplished by
parents or by professionals who come to the home; <as>as,
<ex>home-schooled</ex> students often get higher test scores than those
educated in schools</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>homeschooling</ent>⟦br⟧
